6. **ALWAYS use \`edit\` tool for code changes** ‚ÄĒ if the exact-text match fails, retry with \`write\` (full file content). NEVER fall back to \`bash\` + \`sed\`/\`awk\`. Both \`edit\` and \`write\` trigger lint-guard syntax check.

